Default Paths

/opt/SimpleRemoteControl
/usr/lib/bonobo/servers/GNOME_SimpleRemoteControl.server

To make working the applet, put the files in this 
directory into paths written before with the commands:

cd $dir_where_simplerc_is$/simplerc
sudo mv SimpleRemoteControl /opt
sudo mv GNOME_SimpleRemoteControl.server /usr/lib/bonobo/servers/
or with a superuser nautilus shell

Is a good thing delete any before version's with:
sudo rm /opt/SimpleRemoteControl /usr/lib/bonobo/servers/GNOME_SimpleRemoteControl.server -rf
rm $HOME/.config/simpleremotecontrol

if you are installed from a deb package, remove it with your preferred packet manager

